# ‚öΩ PeakPlay - Soccer Academy Management System

A comprehensive Android application for managing soccer academies, tournaments, teams, and player development. Built with modern Android technologies and Material Design 3.

![Android](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Android-green.svg)
![Kotlin](https://img.shields.io/badge/Language-Kotlin-purple.svg)
![Jetpack Compose](https://img.shields.io/badge/UI-Jetpack%20Compose-blue.svg)
![Min SDK](https://img.shields.io/badge/Min%20SDK-24-orange.svg)

## üì± Features

### For Academy Owners
- *Dashboard*: Real-time statistics for tournaments, players, and staff
- *Tournament Management*: Create, manage, and track soccer tournaments
- *Team Builder*: Organize teams across multiple categories (Kids, Youth, Junior, Senior)
- *Player Assignment*: Search and assign players to teams efficiently
- *Stadium Management*: Manage multiple stadium locations
- *Staff Coordination*: Oversee coaches and referees
- *Social Feed*: Share updates and engage with the community
- *Calendar*: Schedule and track events

### For Coaches
- *Team Overview*: View assigned teams and rosters
- *Game Plans*: Create and manage tactical strategies with formation diagrams
- *Player Development*: Track player progress and performance
- *Match Preparation*: Organize lineups and substitutions

### For Referees
- *Match Officiating*: Real-time match event recording (goals, cards, fouls)
- *Match Schedule*: View assigned matches and tournaments
- *Event Tracking*: Record detailed match statistics

### For Players
- *Profile Management*: Update personal information and stats
- *Team Participation*: Join tournaments and view team schedules
- *Social Networking*: Connect with other players and teams
- *Performance Tracking*: View personal statistics and achievements

## üé® Design

The app features a *premium dark theme* with:
- *Glassmorphism* effects for modern UI elements
- *Vibrant gradients* (Lime to Cyan, Purple to Indigo, Orange to Red)
- *Smooth animations* and transitions
- *Material Design 3* components
- *Responsive layouts* for various screen sizes

## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

### Tech Stack
- *Language*: Kotlin
- *UI Framework*: Jetpack Compose
- *Navigation*: Navigation Compose
- *Networking*: Retrofit 2 + OkHttp
- *Image Loading*: Coil
- *Async*: Kotlin Coroutines
- *Dependency Injection*: Manual (can be upgraded to Hilt/Koin)
- *Storage*: SharedPreferences (via DataStore pattern)

### Project Structure
app/
